				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#9a8456">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1491" y="48" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="388" height="34" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.5019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="right" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：WO[75,50,25,0]</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#eeeeee" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵主飞速旋转双翼，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害；「晦隐」状态下倍率提升，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。吸收元素后</span><span color="#dfbfff">可被附魔</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵主合翼，高高飞起，朝我方角色位置坠下，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害；「晦隐」状态下不施放。吸收元素后</span><span color="#dfbfff">可被附魔</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="735" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「晦隐」状态下，距离较远时，灵主蓄力，并突然重坠，惊起地浪，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/霜夜巡天灵主.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/霜夜巡天灵主.assets/Image_17.png')" x="1392" y="394">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/霜夜巡天灵主.assets/Image_18.png')" x="1391" y="649">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵主进行至多3段的普通攻击，每段均造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害；「晦隐」状态下倍率提升，每段造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。吸收元素后</span><span color="#dfbfff">可被附魔</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵主唤来纯皎的凝晶，朝我方角色如数发射，造成<span color="#b8b8b8">50%,25%,5%</span><span>伤害；<br/>「晦隐」状态下不施放。吸收元素后</span><span color="#dfbfff">可被附魔</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「晦隐」状态下，距离较远时，灵主飞快地挥舞两次，产生两道剑气，分别造成<span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="437" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值低于<span color="#ffcebf">70%</span><span>时，灵主将移至场地中央，进入「</span><span textDecoration="underline">晦隐</span><span>」状态并</span><span color="#bfffbf">清除自身元素及附着</span><span>；召唤16道高速移动的流光，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">70%</span><span>伤害；最后收尾产生爆破，造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span>伤害。此外，「晦隐」状态下，场地内会随机出现1-3枚落月，落地造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
