		<RichText x="1410" y="991" width="438" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「晦隐」状态下，对灵主造成伤害可积攒进度。退出「晦隐」状态后，灵主将吸收<span color="#ffebbf">「晦隐」期间</span><span>所受</span><span color="#ffbfbf">总和最高</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffebbf">伤害属性</span><span>，吸收完毕后灵主将获得</span><span color="#ffbfbf">4单位该元素</span><span>自附着，并</span><span color="#ffbfbf">免疫该元素伤害</span><span>；与龙兽不同的是，若为</span><span color="#ffebbf">月曜反应伤害或物理伤害</span><span>最高，则不会吸收属性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
