		<RichText x="66" y="1128" width="435" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">晦隐：全抗性提升<span color="#ffccbf">120%</span><span>，充能条总量</span><span color="#ff9999">50</span><span>，受到</span><span color="#ffdfbf">月曜反应伤害</span><span>积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">6</span><span>，受到</span><span color="#ffdfbf">非月曜伤害</span><span>积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1</span><span>，充满退出状态，并瘫痪13s；等价于</span><span color="#ffbfbf">50</span><span>次</span><span color="#ffdfbf">非月曜伤害</span><span>或</span><span color="#ffbfbf">9</span><span>次</span><span color="#ffdfbf">月曜伤害</span><span>退出状态，伤害&gt;0的攻击才可充能。(计算总伤害时，月曜伤害按</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1.3倍</span><span>计算)</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
